px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	Theo b&aacute;c sỹ của<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"> White Doctors, </strong>để điều trị mụn hiệu quả bạn cần thực hiện 3 bước sau:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&bull;</strong> Tự đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; t&igrave;nh trạng mụn.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&bull;</strong> T&igrave;m hiểu v&agrave; lựa chọn thuốc c&oacute; th&agrave;nh phần trị mụn ph&ugrave; hợp.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&bull;</strong> Ki&ecirc;n tr&igrave;, tu&acirc;n thủ c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p hỗ trợ điều trị.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 205);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; t&igrave;nh trạng da mụn</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">\r\n	Bạn c&oacute; thể tự &ldquo;kh&aacute;m bệnh&rdquo; cho m&igrave;nh theo c&aacute;c biểu hiện sau đ&acirc;y:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: tahoma, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: norm